OL,3,GWest Midlands
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FBrief bursts
OL,6,Fof sunshine to end the day but often
OL,7,Fcloudy this evening and overnight with
OL,8,Fan increasing chance of showers
OL,9,Fthrough the early hours. Clearer
OL,10,Fperiods developing later and turning
OL,11,Fchilly with patchy grass frost
OL,12,Fpossible in the countryside.
OL,13,
OL,14,CWednesday:FA generally dry day with
OL,15,Fsome sunshine at times, but cloud
OL,16,Fbubbling up through the afternoon.
OL,17,FIsolated showers may break out, but
OL,18,Fmost places will stay dry. Feeling
OL,19,Fcooler.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
